  "prompt": "What are Dream11 revenue streams?",
  "response": "Dream11's primary revenue streams include:\n\n1. Commission from User Contests\n- Charging a platform fee (around 15-20%) on every contest entry\n- Takes a percentage of the total prize pool for each fantasy sports contest\n\n2. Premium Membership\n- Offering paid membership with additional features and benefits\n- Subscription-based model with tiered pricing\n\n3. Advertising and Sponsorships\n- Brand partnerships\n- In-app advertising\n- Sponsorship deals with sports teams and leagues\n\n4. Data Monetization\n- Selling user engagement and sports-related data insights\n- Analytics services for sports organizations\n\n5. Multiple Sports Offerings\n- Fantasy cricket\n- Fantasy football\n- Fantasy kabaddi\n- Fantasy basketball\n- Fantasy baseball\n\nThese revenue streams have helped Dream11 become one of India's leading fantasy sports platforms, generating significant annual revenue through its digital sports engagement model.",
